    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This naturally aspirated powerhouse utilizes six individual throttle bodies to deliver exceptional throttle response and a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. This example has undergone a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a structural subframe reinforcement, addressing the primary mechanical concerns of the chassis. The suspension geometry remains true, offering the precise turn-in and mid-corner stability that defines the M-division's engineering. While the exterior shows honest patina from spirited use, the drivetrain and chassis are dialed in for the serious driver seeking mechanical purity.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
