      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though a few minor stone chips and faint surface marks reflect its honest road history. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean, featuring supple leather seating with only minimal bolster wear on the driver's side. Mechanically, it is in excellent health; I have strictly followed all scheduled maintenance intervals, and the engine delivers smooth, consistent power with no warning lights or unusual noises. All electronics, including the premium infotainment system, navigation, and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. This is a reliable, turn-key car that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
